        depends on MV_ETH_BM_PORT_0 && (MV_ETH_BM_PORT_0_LONG_POOL != MV_ETH_BM_PORT_0_SHORT_POOL)
        range 128 16384
        default 3072
	---help---
        Number of short buffers allocated for this port.

