        int "Number of PMT entries reserved for each flow"
        depends on MV_ETH_PMT
        default 12
        ---help---
        Depend on total number of PMT entries and
        number of flows to be supported.
	MV_ETH_PMT_SIZE >= (MV_ETH_PMT_FLOWS * (MV_ETH_PMT_CMD_PER_FLOW + 1))

